#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:7
msgid ""
"Business expenses may be reimbursed if an individual paid the expense "
"from personal funds."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:9
msgid ""
"This policy establishes the three components required for reimbursement "
"of allowable non-compensation business expenses:"
