#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:54
msgid "DEADLINE TO SUBMIT EXPENSE REPORTS AND DOCUMENTATION"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:56
msgid ""
"Expense Reimbursement DeadlinesTo be reimbursable, business expenses must"
" be properly substantiated and submitted within certain time limitations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:58
msgid ""
"Substantiation for the reimbursement should be submitted within 60 "
"calendar days of when the expenses were incurred. For expenses incurred "
"while traveling, the traveler will have 60 calendar days upon returning "
"from travel to substantiate and submit the expenses."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:59
msgid ""
"If substantiation occurs more than 60 calendar days after the expenses "
"were incurred, the expense reimbursement request must include an "
"explanation for the delay."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:60
msgid ""
"Funds can be reimbursed before travel is completed, with receipts for the"
" travel expenditure. If travel is not completed or is changed to have a "
"lower cost, funds must be returned according to the 'Return of Excess "
"Amounts' section."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:62
msgid "RETURN OF EXCESS AMOUNTS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:64
msgid ""
"Return of excess amounts must be done within 120 days after expenses are "
"paid or incurred."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:66
msgid "Community Initiatives will guide the process for repayment of funds."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/reimbursement-policy.md:68
msgid ""
"If individuals are volunteers, they will be expected to repay “excess "
"amounts” and it may affect their volunteer status with the organization."
msgstr ""

